{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "3. Leelijeetees ar winna Sweh-\ntu Wahrdu/ lai to paschu Sirde\npreezajahs/ kas to KUNGU\nmekle.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "4. Waizajeet pehz ta KUNG-\nGA/ un pehz winna Spehka/\nmeklejeet weenuwehr winna\nWatgu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Peemınneet winna Brih-\nnimus/ ko wiꞥſch irr darrijs/\nwinna Brihnuna-Sihmes un\nwinna Muttes Teefas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Tu Ahbrââma winna Kal-\npa Dsimmus/ juhs Jehkaba\nwinna Iſwehleta Behrni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Wiꞥſch irr tas KUNGS\nmuhfu Deews/ winna Teefas\neet pahr wiﬀu Semmit.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Wiꞥſch peeminn sawu Der-\nribu muhscham/ to Wahrdu/ ko\nwiꞥſch irr eezehtis preekſch tuhſ-\nstofcheem Raddeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. (To Derribu/) ko wiꞥſch\nar Ahbrâamu darrijs/ un winna\nSwehreſchannu ar Ihsaâku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. To wiꞥſch arri Jehkabam\nirr eezehtis par Eikumu/ Israê-\ntam par muhschigu Derribu /\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Sazzidams: Tew doh-\nschu es to Senimi Kanaân/ juh-\nfu Eeimantofchanas Sihmi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Kad tee wehl maſs Pul-\nzinsch bija/ ne dauds un Sweſchi-\nneeki eekſch tahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un staigaja no weenas\nTantas lihds ohtrai/ no weenas\nWaſtības lihds zitteem Laudim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Wiꞥſch ne palaide ne i\nnain tohs apbehdiuaht / wi\nmohzija arri Kehniaus wi-\nlabbad.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Ne aiskarreet mani\nSwaiditus/ un ne darrajt m\nneim Praweescheem Launu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Wiꞥſch aizinaja arri B\ndu pahr to Senimi/ wiꞥſch\nnehme wiﬀu Maises Padohn\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Wiꞥſch fuhtija wiṅ\nBreekſcha weenn Wihrn / J\nseps tappe par Kalpu pahrdoh\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Winna Rahjas tap\nSeekſta spadtitas/ winna M\nfas nahze Dſelsis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Teekans winna Wahr\nnahze/ irr ta KUNGGA Wallo\nwinnu pahrmannijsi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Tas Kehniaſch fuhtija\nun likke winnu atraisiht/\nGauschn Walditajs atlaidē\nWaltā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Wiꞥſch eezehtle to pa\nKungu pahr sawu Namimu\nun par Waldneeku pahr wiﬀ\nsawu Mantu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Ka tas winna Leelns\nKungus faistitu pehz tawu labbi\nPrahtu/ un winna Wezzajeen\nGudribu mahzitu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Pehz nahze Israêls E\ngiptes-Semmê/ un Jehkabs mit\nte par Sweſchineeku eekſch tahē\nSemmes Kam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Un wiꞥſch likke fatons\nLaudis augamo augt/ un darri-\nja tohs jo warrenus/ ne ka wiṅ-\nnu Prettineekus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Wiꞥſch pawehrtija wiṅ\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
